    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款怪物捕捉与<strong>地牢探索</strong>RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经只是和平村民的<strong>安扎</strong>，在大恶魔纳塔斯摧毁他的家园并屠杀家人后，失去了一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >已无所失的他深入危险的地牢，捕捉怪物，不断变强，只为直面夺走他一切的恶魔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854280/extras/a4eb4026d8dbb44697e4e080abfec5b4.webp?t=1771003999\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>怪物捕捉与队伍构建</strong> – 捕捉并训练多种怪物，打造一支强大的队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随机生成的地牢</strong> – 每座地牢都是独一无二的，充满危险的敌人和珍贵的宝藏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战利品与装备</strong> – 寻找稀有物品或购买更好的装备，以强化你队伍的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>稳定成长与逐步提升的难度</strong> – 提升角色与怪物的等级，解锁新区域，挑战强大的首领。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回合制战斗</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854280/extras/2015db2c1f0f3e90fcf03883c74d8374.webp?t=1771003999\" width=616 height=60 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过探索危险的地牢、捕捉怪物，并提升安扎及你队伍的等级来推进游戏进程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854280/extras/b9af487212c7a2926b9ca7294a92da18.avif?t=1771003999\" width=500 height=160 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界地图为半开放设计：随着你不断变强，新的区域将逐步解锁，带来更严峻的挑战与更丰厚的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安扎可以通过提升法力宝珠来解锁新的能力。怪物则会在升级时学会新的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每只怪物都拥有随机的潜力与性格。</p>",
